headline: Republic Services Celebrates Winners of 2025 ROAD-EO National Championship
summary: Republic Services, Inc. (NYSE: RSG), a leader in the environmental services industry, today announced the winners of its 2025 ROAD-EO National Championship. Held every two years in Phoenix, the event recognizes the company's most skilled collection drivers, equipment operators and technicians from across North America.
